Q. How to enable the demo?
A. 
 * install Ubic module from CPAN
 * clone this repo: git clone git@github.com:hayzer/ubic-presentation.git
 * # cd ubic-presentation 
 * # ubic-admin setup (point all directories to ubic-presentation/)
 * the finall result should be 
   # ls ubic-presentation
   bin/  data/  log/  README  service/  slides.html 
 * # ubic status

Good luck!

